{"tid":554922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三題字表慰問","createTime":"2018-02-09T03:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T14:19:46.000Z","uid":32511,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"de920d753ed4db8572ba98114fd4a9eed02aa573","tid":554922,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180209/large/a0605a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180209%2Flarge%2Fa0605a.gif&h=ec89d31a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強震重創花蓮，世界各國第一時間向台灣災民送上溫暖，美國、日本及中國大陸等40國及歐盟表達慰問。日本政府更強調傾力支持，應台灣政府請求，昨天派出專家團隊及新型生命探測儀器赴台救災，民間亦有不少商店及巿民發起募捐，同心協力為花蓮加油。<br />\n<br />\n阿部寬捐71萬賑災<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三昨天就花蓮地震向台灣總統蔡英文致慰問函，強調願提供任何必要協助，隨後還上傳影片，親筆揮毫「台灣加油」。蔡在Twitter特別以日文道謝，指日方慰問「正是所謂患難見真情」，體現台日雙方友情。日本男星阿部寬昨天在台灣出席代言活動，表示對地震造成傷亡感到非常難過，為感謝台灣人以往對日本311地震的捐款，這次想為花蓮大地震盡點心意，個人將捐款1,000萬日圓（下同，約71萬港元）賑災，是首位對花蓮地震捐款的日本藝人。<br />\n此外，日本雅虎網站亦為花蓮地震開設捐款專頁，截至昨晚，累積善款已經逾4,000萬日圓（約285萬港元），捐款人數已經超過5萬，當地更有不少商店擺放籌款箱，並貼出告示為花蓮祈福。<br />\n有指陸委會婉謝中國大陸來台救災，台灣總統府發言人黃重諺昨天回應，台相對發達，救災人員與物資沒有短缺，所以暫時婉謝很多國家，唯一例外是日本，因為對方有深層生命探測儀，能夠加快救出災民。"},{"pid":"a2188250bb00e3ddcdae0b7153e0cd25158bfe10","tid":554922,"uid":32511,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"話時話，總理手字真係寫得幾好，反觀雜種手字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MyNUfBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMyNUfBU.jpg&h=b9e60670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shufalu.com/uploads/allimg/140507/1_140507061951_1-lp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shufalu.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F140507%2F1_140507061951_1-lp.jpg&h=38581b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雜種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dPqbc5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdPqbc5i.jpg&h=295a1475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n智將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GjfxbJP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGjfxbJP.jpg&h=cbfa752f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1590f0d326d8ffcd14f0bb4bbc5cc34c3bbc291","tid":554922,"uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"日本個隻書法字型同本地個隻楷書唔同，成個字好方型好偏，是咩字體？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bba7a62636cb7ac3cea1db05ebc907bc6cecf1","tid":554922,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"尋晚陶傑都有講安倍晉三手字..."},{"pid":"860079d33fa589f5047a52652ca8928c20afbcb9","tid":554922,"uid":33848,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"有指陸委會婉謝中國大陸來台救災，台灣總統府發言人黃重諺昨天回應，台相對發達，救災人員與物資沒有短缺，所以暫時婉謝很多國家，唯一例外是日本，因為對方有深層生命探測儀，能夠加快救出災民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08beaf69e93b3373be260f1e9163058c049ece6","tid":554922,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"嗰手字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e892fe8ab6decde5c2f91af959d2aad99a15bcdf","tid":554922,"uid":39